747
01:29:20,501 --> 01:29:22,457
l'll talk to him.

748
01:29:23,581 --> 01:29:25,537
Your Jesus!

749
01:29:25,661 --> 01:29:27,060
Not ours.

750
01:29:27,181 --> 01:29:29,570
Then whose? Whose?!

751
01:29:29,701 --> 01:29:31,931
Bring him in!

752
01:29:49,781 --> 01:29:52,739
Is this the man you think so dangerous?

753
01:29:53,501 --> 01:29:54,456
